description:
The best Japanese English Dictionary app is now on iPad, iPhone, and iPod touch. It covers over 350,000 words and phrases of the contemporary Japanese language, along with example sentences, audio pronunciations, fastest search speed, flexible search methods, and more … 

REVIEWS

- "Lifesaver helps me everyday ..." - Gary Edwards

- "This is the best dictionary app I've come across." - iCherushi

- "The examples are great! This is the best app so far I had." - Brittany Davis

- "It has romaji which is perfect for me since I can't read very well" - Jaka$d

- "This has become my favorite Japanese-English dictionary." - NotinKSanymore


FEATURES

- Over 350K Japanese words & phrases 
- Example sentences
- Audio pronunciation
- Spelling suggestions 
- Search history record
- Fastest search speed
- Flexible search (by Kanji, Kana, Romaji or English)
- Share learning progress via social networks
- Optimized for iPad, iPhone and iPod touch

If you require any assistance, please contact us at cs@bravolol.com. Remember that we can solve most of the problems, but we cannot respond to comments. Thank you for your support.
